title: Mandrakelinux-10.1-Community-CD1-3
description:
Mandrakelinux 10.1 features the following major softwares:

       Linux Kernel 2.6.8 (and various fixes from 2.6.9rc)
       Xorg 6.7.0
       KDE 3.2.3
       GNOME 2.6
       Glibc 2.3.3, GCC 3.4.1
       Apache 2.0.50, PHP 4.3.8
       MySQL 4.0.18, Samba 3.0.6
       Mozilla 1.7.2, GIMP 2.0.4
       OpenOffice.org 1.1.3

http://www.mandrakelinux.com/en/10.1/features/
